## getData() function

Obtains the value associated with a successful `Result<T>` or throws an exception if the result is an error.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare function getData<T>(result: Result<T>): T;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  result | [Result](./llm-ops.result.md)<!-- -->&lt;T&gt; | The <code>Result&lt;T&gt;</code> from which to obtain the <code>data</code> property. |

**Returns:**

T

The value of the `data` property.
